    "gp_section_535239472732701924": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "f7b2824bb8dd6834f962e5d4e1742eaf3389eb8f6e38e8ae8d1781c814d79ba5_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-6IqZvDyR_text": "<p>Over 57,000 Real Satisfied Customers</p>",
        "gg-lzhCtK-n_text": "<p>&nbsp; 0%</p>",
        "gg-sLpTOIrs_text": "<p>How It Feels and What to Expect</p>",
        "gg0JFO-yEcM_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8ecaa635-3714-4e8e-9906-8479b4b3e2c9.png",
        "gg0Mbk0_MbW_text": "<p>Here’s Your Next Step</p>",
        "gg0uvSjmWDf_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-1164e566-ab0c-4f09-be94-a9ef60ad5c76.png",
        "gg0y7DeYMzr_text": "<p>The authentic SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow is only sold on our official website for only $39.95</p>",
        "gg1VUM96AmK_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow is made of premium materials to provide consistent, reliable support and lasting comfort.</p>",
        "gg1ZTzCEOvP_text": "<p>4.8 out of 5</p>",
        "gg1fg54qodK_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>Day 14:</strong></span> At two weeks, you might find your posture improved as the pillow helps encourage your muscles to maintain proper alignment. Nights of sleep get longer with less waking up, and your ability to perform daily activities could increase.</p>",
        "gg2GbzcbiVU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-774247ee-6407-4926-8ca5-e77215af0472.png",
        "gg2t_R48rWQ_text": "<p>90%</p>",
        "gg3hMtPO1WF_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-ac376fcb-93e3-44ab-b806-b3776be94c38.png",
        "gg3ic8VwSJq_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>Day 1:</strong></span> From the very first use, you may notice a reduction in discomfort and a better night's sleep without many interruptions.</p>",
        "gg475vAy_v6_text": "<p>3 Star</p>",
        "gg4xxxACX_V_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:#FFBF00;\">If you suffer from Sciatica pain in your lower back, hips, or legs,</span> <span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,255,255,0);\">leading to sleepless nights and waking up stiff and sore, </span>read this short article right now before you do anything else.</p>",
        "gg5odf7pNVp_text": "<p>5.0</p>",
        "gg6owctFm6d_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8d759f93-dca8-483c-84a6-6fdfde7b1089.webp",
        "gg7BmL-pOf5_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-7c8734ef-2aa6-49ff-a685-3b012371254a.png",
        "gg7PP_PdUoQ_text": "<p>This reduction in compression allows your muscles and discs to relax and recover naturally, giving you relief from that burning, stabbing pain you feel when you wake up.</p>",
        "gg7T9_xAWJ1_text": "<p>And while you may think it’s just part of getting older, the truth is, the way you sleep could be the real problem.</p>",
        "gg7dN0O3K9Z_text": "<p>So if you know anyone who could benefit from the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow.</p>",
        "gg7lnWFIkKi_text": "<p>There are plenty of pillows that claim to help with sleep and pain relief, but few deliver on those promises like the <i>SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow</i>. What sets it apart?</p>",
        "gg82fWlvyF4_text": "<p>These discs help your spine move and absorb pressure. <strong>But when you sleep in a misalignment position</strong>, the weight of your body can push down too hard on these discs, causing pain or even leading to bigger problems like herniated discs.</p>",
        "gg8p2-eUE0s_text": "<p>After the first night of using SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow, you'll notice a big difference in how well you slept. The unqiue design ensures your spine is aligned and stable. As you finally align your spinal discs properly, you’ll experience a gentle, peaceful sensation that also <strong>helps you fall asleep pain-free</strong>.</p>",
        "gg96ubj9Zf6_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/f560d53c857b483d9f37b2e6ad9f9822.mp4",
        "gg96ubj9Zf6_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg96ubj9Zf6_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg9bFJbXXEN_text": "<p>Comfort</p>",
        "gg9t23R6ZNB_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/e1ae5ea6d685432d997c4a85215930b1.mp4",
        "gg9t23R6ZNB_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg9t23R6ZNB_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggA2ElEw_Qk_text": "<p>I recommend you DO NOT leave this page… Because this may be <strong>THE ONLY CHANCE</strong> to get the relief you were praying for.</p>",
        "ggA9IeRVVkU_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/5a04680dc4e14541a23d15bdc57d9291.mp4",
        "ggA9IeRVVkU_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggA9IeRVVkU_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggAAICOK6bL_text": "<p>Sciatica can be a real nightmare—if you’ve ever felt that burning pain starting in your lower back or hip and running down your leg, you know how bad it can get.</p>",
        "ggAfegIm6u1_text": "<p><strong>A WHOLE -50% OFF - only today, so you can grab your Alignment Pillow for less.</strong></p>",
        "ggAiumAnsu7_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b585c819-788e-4b54-b8c2-3ff8daa9b9ab.png",
        "ggAiz-Ap8Do_text": "<p>Second, because <strong>it makes a wonderful gift for your spouse</strong>. And it’s far more fun to get Aligned together at the same time.</p>",
        "ggB7BGfliF__srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-9bb9b59b-e9f5-43be-8cff-78dd8743409b.png",
        "ggBBhHs9iym_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://ucarecdn.com/f0fd2cb0-0ec0-47b9-9ade-60feba9841e5/-/format/auto/-/preview/1500x1500/-/quality/lighter/3%20_2_.png",
        "ggBxFcQqeeP_text": "<p>Most of his patients suffer from issues that stem from years of <strong>poor sleeping positions</strong> and insufficient support.</p>",
        "ggC713UQZ0J_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:#FFBF00;\">And that is why We Priced It At 1/2</span> of What All the Experts Recommended</p>",
        "ggCEXcsnt2K_text": "<p>Let’s face it—waking up in pain is no way to start your day.</p>",
        "ggCGayFa8Wz_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>Day 7:</strong></span> By the end of the first week, the consistent nighttime support may contribute to reducing your discomfort completely. You might feel more mobile and possibly less dependent on pain relief methods.</p>",
        "ggC_HLz3Nt1_text": "<p>5.0</p>",
        "ggCjfJvN5Wr_text": "<p>And the only goal with this pillow is to help as many people as possible.</p>",
        "ggCuPVsYfdL_text": "<p>Did you know that how you sleep can mess up your back and hips?&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggDJwm5TAtB_text": "<p>Trusted By Medical Experts</p>",
        "ggDTVeHMtS2_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/15f4ee7366ea4ba6b438422ab0b270cf.mp4",
        "ggDTVeHMtS2_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggDTVeHMtS2_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggDrmdSIbID_text": "<p>Just imagine how your life would look like:</p>",
        "ggDu3u686nL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-880a17da-70f4-49ac-9175-1e3b4807227f.png",
        "ggDxeLdQkP4_text": "<p>Price</p>",
        "ggE15XdiBTy_text": "4,684 Ratings",
        "ggEQocTiPmV_text": "<p>No special exercise plan or strict schedule like with other health solutions, no need to change any of your routines either. And as a result you will reap the sleep and<strong> relief benefits for the WHOLE night</strong>.</p>",
        "ggEw6PwgKBF_text": "<p>Real People, Real Relief</p>",
        "ggFBRCfbnh3_text": "<p><strong>Most people end up ordering multiple S Pillows.</strong></p>",
        "ggFQcmgpimu_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8d759f93-dca8-483c-84a6-6fdfde7b1089.webp",
        "ggGRaNAAs7-_text": "<p>And I’m confident that it’s going to help you too.</p>",
        "ggGVhE9UP0v_text": "<p>4.8</p>",
        "ggGkHY4dMUC_text": "<p>But I hate to admit that we are currently failing at that - <strong>the demand is just too big</strong>.</p>",
        "ggGm8ln32o7_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-7f8ec3e6-1a39-4ee6-b91c-fb705c8067b0.png",
        "ggGrSH_EtTz_text": "<p>Quality</p>",
        "ggGtlIzM5XX_text": "<p>5.0</p>",
        "ggHWxkqsKz9_text": "<p>Guaranteed high quality</p>",
        "ggHhh9o2n5H_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/44f8b6872c5d4fba98ac18a6118c861a.mp4",
        "ggHhh9o2n5H_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggHhh9o2n5H_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggHmNJ-3dIb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8d759f93-dca8-483c-84a6-6fdfde7b1089.webp",
        "ggHz6J_p85b_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-78c6c65c-c0c4-482c-9df8-ffc77a2ffb88.png",
        "ggI1umGb4p2_text": "<p><strong>If you’re a side sleeper</strong>, like many of us, you might be putting pressure on your spine without even knowing it.</p>",
        "ggI9wifD87C_text": "<p>How Sleeping the Wrong Way Can Damage Your Back and Hips</p>",
        "ggIDaynodIh_text": "<p>Your spine is made up of bones that have little cushions (called discs) between them.</p>",
        "ggIEcUkNB1k_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/0260b19487254840b1feb6d101cc145d.mp4",
        "ggIEcUkNB1k_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggIEcUkNB1k_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggIYpqjeYTB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4f81447a-884d-40b9-ac8c-abef62b4e870.png",
        "ggKmy0OQCUq_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-111e5ffe-2969-4b8c-bbbd-ececa9323319.png",
        "ggLBogxD-ED_text": "<p>90-Night Money Back Guarantee</p>",
        "ggLDkfOPlsA_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/3dd82280636141758421ac1dd85754ab.mp4",
        "ggLDkfOPlsA_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggLDkfOPlsA_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggLE1HiR_pg_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-d8f79620-26aa-44d0-b255-c9a614cd2079.png",
        "ggLczMDdfzG_text": "<p>Say Goodbye to Pinched Nerves, Hip Pain, and Back Discomfort</p>",
        "ggLuejGCamZ_text": "<p>Folks who have tested the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow and experienced the relief are now asking us for more devices for their families and friends.</p>",
        "ggMItpKCkbc_text": "<p>Over time, this also leads to nerve problems like sciatica, where the big nerve that runs from your lower back to your legs gets pinched, <strong>causing sharp shooting pain or a constant dull ache.</strong></p>",
        "ggMNpygy9kE_text": "<p>That’s where the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow comes in—this isn’t just a regular pillow; it’s a <strong>scientifically designed solution to help align your spine, reduce pain, and prevent further damage.</strong></p>",
        "ggMwomynm1s_text": "<p><strong>All this makes our stock run out quickly every time we get a new shipment.</strong></p>",
        "ggNau1K7Ir2_text": "<p>4 Star</p>",
        "ggOAT_PYT5n_text": "<p>Then, select the region you’re in and add the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow to your cart.</p>",
        "ggOqIZEMM3v_text": "<p>1 Star</p>",
        "ggQHx3nB57F_text": "<p>With the right level of firmness and support, you could keep your spine in their correct positions, distributing pressure evenly across your back rather than concentrating it on specific areas.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggQPCGIh3R1_text": "<p><strong>You can prevent this from happening by maintaining proper spine alignment.</strong></p>",
        "ggQ_ZqK6AxA_text": "<p>This would mean less pain, fewer flare-ups, and a much better chance of waking up feeling refreshed, instead of dreading the day ahead.</p>",
        "ggQiDl3-5ob_text": "<p>Once we run out of stock…</p>",
        "ggQnOM32ssM_text": "<p>And guess what? You'll probably use it way more than that.</p>",
        "ggQpqedqKxP_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/5bfd4c576fc24e76a1936845cedb8c19.mp4",
        "ggQpqedqKxP_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggQpqedqKxP_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggRPepLCka5_text": "<p>To put it into perspective, when SmoothSpine hired business &amp; marketing consultants to help us launch the pillow to the market, they told them to charge $80.</p>",
        "ggRrargy9cE_text": "<p>Why the <a href=\"https://smoothspine.com/products/pres-alp\"><u>SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow</u></a> Stands Out</p>",
        "ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_0": "<p><strong>Optimal Spine Alignment:</strong> Ensures your spine remains aligned throughout the night, relieving pressure on intervertebral discs.</p>",
        "ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_1": "<p><strong>Targeted Pain Relief:</strong> Reduces lower back pain, hip discomfort, and sciatica by preventing nerve impingement.</p>",
        "ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_2": "<p><strong>Moves With You:</strong> Stays in place when turning over, so you don&#039;t wake up having to readjust it.</p>",
        "ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_3": "<p><strong>Perfect Firmness:</strong> Strikes the ideal balance between softness and support, cradling your body without collapsing under your weight.</p>",
        "ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_4": "<p><strong>Breathable, Cool Design:</strong> Stays cool throughout the night, preventing heat build-up that can disturb sleep.</p>",
        "ggSDELymd7F_text": "<p><strong>So if you are serious about reducing pain and discomfort in your hips and lower back…</strong></p>",
        "ggSiqFIbMxg_text": "<p>AS SEEN ON&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggTpmUydUgo_text": "<p>5 Star</p>",
        "ggU189ePJgv_text": "<p>Not Available in Normal Stores!</p>",
        "ggUdLMEjEBz_text": "Leading Physical Therapy Specialist: <strong>This Is The Best Way to Sleep Pain-Free Through The Night</strong>",
        "ggV-NkPO7Iq_text": "<p>By correcting poor posture, relieving pressure on your discs, and reducing nerve impingement, this pillow helps you <strong>sleep better and live pain-free</strong>.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggV3rzNuWDx_text": "By W. Patton <i>(Medical Reporter)</i>",
        "ggWB0CXWiHs_text": "<p>Now, if you are reading this article, it means that we probably have a few pillows left in stock, otherwise, we would’ve taken the page down.</p>",
        "ggWbf_6GsVy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f5c3a167-1592-4357-b05d-0dc9ad2d5ea9.png",
        "ggWu3B-Sa4N_text": "<p>&nbsp; 2%</p>",
        "ggYTmbm5iFw_text": "<p>Sleeping without proper support causes your spine to fall out of alignment, which puts pressure on your spinal discs, and results in <strong>agonizing pain in your lower back and hips.</strong></p>",
        "ggYjtVoUMjq_text": "<p><strong>That's only a fraction of the cost of what you would spend for therapy - $100s of dollar just per one session!</strong></p>",
