        "gghT_gjY1FV_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggi6Cz2z6R1_text": "<p>A major issue for most side sleepers is hip pain, which is often caused by bone-on-bone contact or poor support for the lower body.</p>",
